  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purposes of this study is to determine whether Heparin Binding Protein (HBP) can be used
      as a marker of severe sepsis (including septic shock) in patients presenting to the emergency
      department with suspected infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
